;; -*- outline -*-

* Bugfix
** Allow the working of cl-objc on a read-only installation (i.e. without framework caching)

** Support for Variadic ObjC methods

** Remove warnings in test suite :runtime

** Change accessors -> readers when a write is undefined, or write the appropriate writer

* Docs & Examples
** Update the docs: add a tutorial on the clos interface

** Add more examples (one using the clos interface)

** Use cl-launch for the examples

* New minor features

** Cache protocol names per framework

** Make ensure-objc-class try to add the ivars to a class if the definition is the same as previous

** Add an objc-let* macro

** README file

** Better error signaling if wrong input to functions is passed

* New major features

** Define a variadic defun to call foreign functions instead of using a variadic macro

** Complete the ObjC CLOS interface (objc ivars in slots, mixed slots, defmethod mixed)

** Support for the call to super

** Let user add effective protocols to classes

** Integration with XCode
